<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>101</hymn_number>
<author>J. Foster</author>
<title>Ny hazo fijaliana FFPM101</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ny hazo fijaliana,
 Ry Jeso Tomponay,
 Dia tena fitoriana
 Fa tianao 'zahay.

[V2]
 Ny hazo fijaliana
 Dia manambara izao
 Fa be ny fahoriana
 Nihatra taminao.

[V3]
 Ny hazo fijaliana
 No mampiseho koa
 Fa tokony hariana
 Ny ota mahavoa.

[V4]
 Isaoranay dia isaoranay
 Hianao, ry Tomponay,
 Fa be ny fitiavana
 Nataonao taminay.</lyrics>
</song>